20:41.319 --> 20:42.420
It's a form of mandrake.

20:43.621 --> 20:45.903
But it's sold as a drug.

20:45.923 --> 20:47.605
Well, it's the best drug there is.

20:47.645 --> 20:49.567
It kills any of you.

20:49.587 --> 20:50.948
Look at that.

20:50.968 --> 20:52.309
Yeah, look at that thing.

20:54.111 --> 20:56.653
Well, they have all kinds of stores.

20:56.733 --> 20:57.814
It's still very popular in China.

20:59.336 --> 20:59.896
Oh, God, yeah.

20:59.916 --> 21:01.778
Oh, it's in LA, too.

