This is a little frozen box.

21:13.484 --> 21:17.149
And this is a geometron tablet.

21:17.169 --> 21:27.302
And so happens I have a nephew, who is now a professor of such stuff at Harvard.

21:27.882 --> 21:30.426
And among other things, he reads these.

21:30.446 --> 21:30.706
Oh!

21:31.607 --> 21:33.409
Did he give you, would he be able to play for it?

21:33.569 --> 21:33.790
Yeah.

21:34.090 --> 21:34.411
Oh, he did.

