It's a list of animals that some storekeeper probably sold one day.

21:38.950 --> 21:41.193
Seven chickens, one cow, two goats.

21:41.213 --> 21:42.035
They kept all their records.

21:42.055 --> 21:43.116
This is pre-paper.

21:43.417 --> 21:43.817
Right.

21:43.837 --> 21:44.919
But they didn't write on paper.

21:44.979 --> 21:45.840
They didn't have paper.

21:46.541 --> 21:47.403
Yeah, it's wonderful.

21:47.423 --> 21:48.604
This is how old, do you figure?

21:49.225 --> 21:53.191
Better than 3,000 years old.

21:53.431 --> 21:56.836
Did they bake those, or did they... Oh, yeah, this is baked.

