This is palm leaf.

22:39.840 --> 22:40.001
Palm?

22:41.523 --> 22:43.785
Some kind of palm leaf.

22:43.845 --> 22:45.587
How old is it?

22:45.608 --> 22:47.510
A couple of hundred years.

22:48.331 --> 22:48.771
About that.

22:49.793 --> 22:54.238
Here's another one.

22:54.278 --> 22:56.541
So that's the surface that they use in Indonesia?

22:56.561 --> 22:58.283
Palm leaf, yeah.

22:59.275 --> 23:00.777
Look at the delicacy.

